title: Recap of Week Zero and a Preview of Week One
description:
Wendi Nix, Sam Acho and Greg McElroy took a deep dive into Scott Frost's future at Nebraska. Plus, what teams still haven't announced their starting quarterbacks? Also, can Ohio State keep their winning streak alive against Notre Dame?
